divs: sighting detailson the 28\04\13 i discovered i can do time lapse photography with my new nikon d5100. on my third series of shots of clouds moving across the sky (500 pics, 10 secs apart, shutter speed 1\400 sec) i made into a vid. anyway i was watching the vid when i saw a black spot at top of screen. i finally found the one and only frame and i couldn't believe my eyes. have a look, see what you think. this is a legit pic. the white spec below is a jet liner. the image was taken at 1148am on 28\04\13. the camera was facing almost directly east. i live in new beith, logan, qld. not very far from greenbank army camp. your opinion and further analysis by other ufo experts would be very appreciated.
Summary: Doing timelapse of clouds, one frame has ufo
